      "factId": "hz.web.e848a1b5b41c9b1b.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "I absolutely recommend it and right now it's on sale on Steam for $6.99 USD!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=\"https://bear-images.sfo2.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/binarydigit/on-together-id.webp\" alt=\"on-together-ID\" /&gt; &lt;img src=\"https://bear-images.sfo2.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/binarydigit/on-together-2.webp\" alt=\"on-together-2\" /&gt; &lt;img src=\"https://bear-images.sfo2.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/binarydigit/on-together-3.webp\" alt=\"on-together-3\" /&gt; &lt;img src=\"https://bear-images.sfo2.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/binarydigit/on-together-4.webp\" alt=\"on-together-4\" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;There are tons of little areas on the map that you can find to do different activities to earn in-game currency (tickets) and unlock clothing, pets, and accessories for your desk.",
